            "unit": "ml",
            "value": 1
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "annotations": {
          "text": "Add 1 ml PFA (prewarmed in a 37 °C water bath) and incubate the tube at RT for 30–60 min. CRITICAL STEP Do not exceed the time of PFA fixation above 1 h since this will lead to high autofluorescence. Use with 37 °C water bath warmed PFA to fix the organoids to enhance penetration of PFA and preserve the cytoskeleton of the cells, since cold treatment leads to depolymerization of microtubules."
        },
        "id": "s5",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "id": "s1",
            "kind": "sample"
          }
        ],
        "op": "transfer",
        "outputs": [
